{"cursor":"11408","size":15,"audio":[],"currentlang":"en","article":"\n{{Infobox company\n| name = Broad Group logo = caption = type = genre = fate = predecessor =\n| successor = foundation = 1988 founder = Zhang Yue defunct = location_city =\n| Changsha, Hunan location_country = China location = locations = area_served =\n| key_people = Zhang Yue (Chairman & CEO) industry = Manufacturing Construction \nEnergy Services\n| products = Absorption chiller Air-conditioning Sustainable\n| building Air purifier services = Energy Services revenue = 900 million\n| USD (2007) operating_income = net_income = aum = assets\n| = equity = owner = num_employees = parent = divisions = subsid = Broad\n| Sustainable Building\nBroad Air Conditioning\n| homepage = http://www.broad.com http://www.broadusa.com footnotes =\n| intl = yes\n}}\n\n'Broad Group' is a private company based in Changsha, China. Since 1996, it has\nbeen the global leader in manufacturing central air conditioning non-electric\nabsorption chillers that are powered by natural gas and waste heat. Broad Group\ncurrently export products to over 60 countries. It was Shanghai Expo 2010's only global official partner that was a\nChinese private enterprise and the exclusive supplier of central air\nconditioning, ventilation and air purification products for the\nevent.\n\nBroad is one of the few Chinese manufacturing companies that has been widely\nrecognized for its green policies and commitment to countering climate change.\nIt has expanded its business in recent years to include other energy saving\nproducts and sustainable buildings through its subsidiary Broad Sustainable\nBuilding, and achieved the feat of building a 15-story tall hotel in 6 days,\nwhich received 2 million views in the first 10 days after being released on\nYouTube. CNNGo.com http://www.cnngo.com/shanghai/life/build-hotel-six-days-china-it-can-and-has-\nbeen-done-673433#ixzz1SiuR5nHi|url=http://www.cnngo.com/shanghai/life/build-\nhotel-six-days-china-i